Package by.zyablov.airlinecompany.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AircraftBuilderBehavior
    Interface AircraftBuilderBehavior creates and initializes fields of Aircraft objects.
    BuilderBehavior
    Interface BuilderBehavior is used to create objects of different classes with many fields.
    CompanyBuilderBehavior
    Interface CompanyBuilderBehavior is used to create and initialize fields of Company object.
    FileAircraftsReaderable
    Interface FileAircraftsReaderable is used to read Aircraft objects from file.
    FileAircraftsWriterable
    Interface FileAircraftsWriterable is used to write Aircraft objects to file.
    Measureable
    Interface Measureable represents methods of a physical values.
    NewAircraftConsoleCreatorBehavior
    Interface NewAircraftConsoleCreatorBehavior uses to create a new Aircraft objects by user console.
    UniqueAircraftTechDataBehavior
    Interface UniqueAircraftTechDataBehavior represents a unique technical data information for AirlinerAircraft and CargoAircraft classes.
